{"id": 1658, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪些事情对你来说是“小确治愈”的？", "description": "不一定非要是“吃吃吃”和“买买买”啊！（题图来自：Jill Wellington）", "record_count": 5944, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170427151402Ow5gkSqh18zWmXt7.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-30T17:00:26Z", "options": [{"id": 198400, "content": "办公桌捯饬干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 226, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931774}, {"id": 198656, "content": "吃好吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018299}, {"id": 198401, "content": "數錢咯。數完了再數第二遍。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256}, {"id": 198657, "content": "午后的阳光", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668499}, {"id": 198913, "content": "爬上山 大口呼吸的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 899167}, {"id": 198402, "content": "抱着女朋友香香睡一晚\n(¦3[▓▓]\n\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 198658, "content": "把第二天要办的事带出门的东西都收拾好躺在床上偷着乐的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010858}, {"id": 199170, "content": "什么都比不上吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020239}, {"id": 198659, "content": "工作的时候听见谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879398}, {"id": 199427, "content": "整理出好看的笔记", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1013937}, {"id": 199939, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170503195559z2QHRVqbCSynvUZ8.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022018}, {"id": 200707, "content": "在外面吃饭，居然喝到米汤。（现在都用电饭煲做饭已经没有米汤了）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807000}, {"id": 198660, "content": "每次把一个星期的衣服洗完的时候。恩，我是个男的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019647}, {"id": 199172, "content": "看到可爱的句子 “我想起小刺猬就感觉它的身后一定有红果果”", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020242}, {"id": 200452, "content": "一首歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004783}, {"id": 200964, "content": "特别沮丧的时候，有人给你温暖一笑", "image": "img/option/option/20170505193632IrW0gtQR7cAL9ikV", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024005}, {"id": 198405, "content": "安静的听歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1001492}, {"id": 198661, "content": "写日记", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1002327}, {"id": 199429, "content": "有钱吃吃吃和买买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913669}, {"id": 201733, "content": "有个人听我说说话，一个人就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026424}, {"id": 198406, "content": "看见喜欢的动漫人物周边，手办，心情很糟也会平静下来", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018207}, {"id": 198662, "content": "看到理解我的文字，而不是一味责怪", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019654}, {"id": 199174, "content": "两岁的女儿枕在我肚子上看卡通", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927135}, {"id": 200198, "content": "早上把被子晒出去 晚上睡觉的时候一股暖洋洋的阳光味", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022423}, {"id": 204550, "content": "心情很down的时候，突然看到一抹美丽的夕阳美景…\n\n因为工作琐事，刚发完火，同事送来好吃的水果…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034126}, {"id": 197639, "content": "每天打开亚马逊kindle书店，不用买，看一看就很舒爽，不过要避开阿弥陀佛么么哒这种", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 198407, "content": "她笑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913020}, {"id": 198663, "content": "有次喝大了 把领居家摆在走廊的花 从一楼搬到七楼 酒醒莫名其妙看到有花 ...默默到又从七楼搬下去.邻居小哥哥居然说送你了....盛情难却 我只好又搬到七楼....（我也很绝望呀！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019656}, {"id": 198919, "content": "拿起笔，听着广播，写一写心中的事，听一听世上的事。世界很小，只有我在其中；世界很大，我只是其中之一。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945317}, {"id": 199175, "content": "A cup of wine", "image": "img/option/option/20170502010359Xko9lnxu2Ugf08zH.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012072}, {"id": 199431, "content": "跟?玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814077}, {"id": 201991, "content": "网络时代?只需一部手机?就多一份收入，多一份任性?微信咨询2227887341?每天至少50-300+，上不封顶，半月轻松入2000+?你不比别人差❗️差别就在于你缺少一个有实力的团队和一颗赚钱的心❤️", "image": "img/option/option/20170509081059Nzmba2YAu5R0dBU3.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027056}, {"id": 202759, "content": "自己逗一下自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029387}, {"id": 197640, "content": "把我男朋友攒在家里的没用玩意儿都扔了", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 198408, "content": "她笑了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913020}, {"id": 198664, "content": "看到一段治愈系文字。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865541}, {"id": 199176, "content": "得到了可以去看偶像的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933101}, {"id": 199432, "content": "想吃什么东西的时候手边刚好有。或者热到爆炸的时候喝冰的仙草鲜爽", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021072}, {"id": 197641, "content": "看完买不起的小破烂房子，打开好好住看看怎么改造，心情就好多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 198409, "content": "不漏点的风情写真比日本动作片好看多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 875173}, {"id": 198665, "content": "听到喜欢的人又出了新歌，就很开心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1019661}, {"id": 199433, "content": "有人和你说晚安和早上好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021076}, {"id": 203529, "content": "坐在公交车最后一排靠窗的位置 稍稍打开一点窗  漏出一点风  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 980484}, {"id": 197642, "content": "搜那种两三千的山间民宿看，不用去住，看看就挺治愈", "image": null, "praise_count": 131, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118131}, {"id": 198410, "content": "和林友欣在一起\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994158}, {"id": 198666, "content": "甜点", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671248}, {"id": 198411, "content": "洗澡澡?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407163}, {"id": 198667, "content": "运动到大汗淋漓", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671248}, {"id": 199435, "content": "和一个喜欢的人（不一定是男女朋友）聊天，聊到天黑，聊到天亮！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984344}, {"id": 206859, "content": "睡觉?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908163}]}